{
  "stem": "8352.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, right, but I could see-- I could see those-- [SIGHS] those police catching a Jew on the street and take a knife and just pull the beard and-- and cut it with  a knife and just hurting him.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I saw it with my own eyes quite often-- for no reason.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We start to get very scary.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were very afraid of that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was going to be later on we started thinking about it, what was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [SIGHS] after all those things, it was very scary life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We couldn't go to the shul anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't-- they didn't let us go certain places.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Then it came that we-- I have to start to going into the-- into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they started taking us away in 1944.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We lived like that till about-- the Germans came in very late to our country.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were the last ones that the Germans occupied at the town there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The-- it was a tough life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It wasn't easy-- a scary life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then in 1944, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the Hungarians told us we have to meet at the schoolyard.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And we will be taken away to a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "No, the Germans came in first. 1944, the Germans came in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And as soon as they came in, they went to the mayor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they got all the Jewish names from the-- from the-- from the little village there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Came a bulletin-- and they said that we can take 20, 25 kilos with us-- belongings, food, whatever we want to-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and meet in the school yard.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Leave everything the way it is in the house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we will be assembling there.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
